[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy, 13, critical after being hit by two cars

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A 13-year-old boy is in a critical condition in hospital in Glasgow after being hit by at least two cars.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The boy was crossing Dumbarton Road in Scotstoun when he was hit by an Audi and a Ford Fiesta at about 14:40.
He was taken to the Queen Elizabeth University Hospital.
